     </li>
     <li>
      Both Voidtrain and Lost in Random: The Eternal Die will join many other titles coming to the service next year.
     </li>
     <li>
      Next year will be packed for Game Pass subscribers, with big-name titles like Fable, Expedition 33, and Doom: The Dark Ages slated to join the service.
