 <p>
  <strong>
   <em>
    Fallout 76
   </em>
  </strong>
  is getting an update with Gleaming Depths at the end of the year, bringing a fresh new chapter to Bethesda's multiplayer addition to the
  <em>
   Fallout
  </em>
  franchise.
  <em>
   Fallout 76
  </em>
  showcases a nuclear-ravaged wasteland set in the mountains of Appalachia, which has proven to be a wonderful setting to explore. As of now, Gleaming Depths has merely been teased, but there will hopefully be more on the horizon that involves an underserved area of the map.
 </p>
 <!-- No repeatable ad for zone: character count repeatable. -->
 <!-- Repeatable debug data: {"injection":"none","adPosition":1,"startingPoint":0,"skipEvery":null,"nbrPlacementFilledEachSkip":1,"nbrPlacementsScanned":1,"ruleCount":900,"degradationStartingPoint":1,"stopAds":null,"actualCount":457} -->
