 <p>
  Out of all the locations in
  <em>
   Fallout 76
  </em>
  , the Ash Heap is one of the most hazardous areas on the map. The location has gained its name for a very good reason. Pillars of billowing smoke and cinders permeate the area, making it a serious health risk. From Wendigos to various Mutants, the Ash Heap is home to some horrifying creatures, but there is hopefully more to the area than meets the eye.
