 <p>
  The Ash Heap has to be more than just a smoldering wasteland. If
  <em>
   Fallout 76
  </em>
  wants to breathe some new life into the map, turning this often-avoided area into a central focus of Gleaming Depths would be an exciting change of pace. Not only would it entice players to explore the Ash Heap, it would provide Gleaming Depths with the perfect stage to offer an exciting hunt for Ultracite while also providing an intense environmental challenge.
  <em>
   Fallout 76
  </em>
  is filled with valuable items, and there is no telling what other great rewards could be hidden underneath the Ash Heap.
